&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://comterman.tistory.com/320&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;2012/12/18 - 환골탈태한 구식 턴테이블 DUAL 1019, 만만치 않았던 복원기&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
